---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Esther K. Shin, LMFT — compassionate relational therapy for individuals, couples, and families in Orange County, CA.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section text-center" style="padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
        <img src="/images/eks-logo.png" alt="Esther K. Shin Therapy Logo" style="max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto;" />
      </div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.6rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 1rem;">
        welcome
      </h1>
      <p style="max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem;">
        Life can be filled with many stressors impacting our mental, emotional, physical, and relational health. No matter where you are in life, you are not meant to go through it alone.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Your Trusted Relational Resource -->
  <section class="section section-alt text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden;">
        <img src="/images/eks-trusted.jpg" alt="Esther K. Shin, LMFT" style="width: 100%; height: auto;" />
      </div>
      <h2>Your Trusted Relational Resource</h2>
      <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 1rem;">Licensed Marriage and Family Therapist</p>
      <p style="max-width: 580px; margin: 1.5rem auto;">
        Hello. I am glad you are here in your first step in your journey towards healing and growth. It is my privilege to join alongside you in paving your life towards health, healing, and wholeness.
      </p>
      <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline">Get to Know Esther</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Where To Begin -->
  <section class="section text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Where To Begin?</h2>
      <p style="max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
        Starting therapy can be daunting. You've already taken a brave first step looking into therapy. I encourage you to take another step to reach out. Therapy could be a safe and non-judgmental space you need — one where you can develop a deep understanding of yourself and find relief from the emotional pain you carry.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Let's Connect</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Behind The Logo -->
  <section class="section section-alt text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Behind The Logo</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 300px; margin: 2rem auto;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
          <!-- Lotus flower -->
          <ellipse cx="80" cy="120" rx="48" ry="28" fill="none" stroke="#c4956a" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(-20, 80, 120)" opacity="0.6"/>
          <ellipse cx="120" cy="120" rx="48" ry="28" fill="none" stroke="#c4956a" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(20, 120, 120)" opacity="0.6"/>
          <ellipse cx="100" cy="130" rx="40" ry="25" fill="none" stroke="#c4956a" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.7"/>
          <ellipse cx="100" cy="100" rx="20" ry="35" fill="none" stroke="#c4956a" stroke-width="2"/>
          <!-- Marigold -->
          <circle cx="130" cy="70" r="28" fill="none" stroke="#d4a373" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
          <circle cx="130" cy="70" r="18" fill="none" stroke="#d4a373" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.8"/>
          <circle cx="130" cy="70" r="8" fill="#d4a373" opacity="0.4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-style: italic; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        The logo is comprised of two flowers — a lotus and a marigold. The lotus symbolizes compassion, resilience, transformation, and rebirth. The marigold represents power, strength, and the light that lives inside a person.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-muted" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 1.5rem auto 0;">
        My hope is that you would come to experience and embody these various milestones within yourself as we journey towards health, healing, and wholeness.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
